    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#fn> "Open Data FPS BOSA DG SD"@en, "Open Data FOD BOSA DG VD"@nl, "Open Data SPF BOSA DG SD"@fr, "Open Data FÖD BOSA DG VD"@de;
