    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://eurovoc.europa.eu/2278>, <http://eurovoc.europa.eu/4100>, <http://eurovoc.europa.eu/2840>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/1912>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/1708>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/5507>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/6743>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/6740>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/3974>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/3977>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/10066>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/538>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/11375>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/3712>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/theme/ps>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialScope/regional>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialDataServiceCategory/infoFeatureAccessService>;
