<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#4d33f707a6d8f72af94775a2434c32a1>.
<#4d33f707a6d8f72af94775a2434c32a1> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/dataset/brussels/da181eac-0756-11f1-8373-900f0cda5d5b>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-06-15T15:38:07.146Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#4d33f707a6d8f72af94775a2434c32a1> {
<http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/dataset/brussels/da181eac-0756-11f1-8373-900f0cda5d5b> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#DataService>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "da181eac-0756-11f1-8373-900f0cda5d5b";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Betegeld raadpleegdienst - Raster"@nl, "Service de visualisation tuilé – Raster"@fr, "Tiled view service - Raster"@en, "Kachelblick-Service - Raster"@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Deze betegeld raadpleegdienst maakt het mogelijk om geo-gerefereerde tegels te verkrijgen van de rasterdatasets die deel uitmaken van de UrbIS-reeks.\nDeze service wordt periodiek bijgewerkt op basis van de overeenkomstige lagen van de Raadpleegdienst - Raster. Het gebruik van deze service wordt aanbevolen voor alle viewers en front-endapplicaties."@nl, "Ce service de visualisationtuilé permet d'obtenir des tuiles géo-référencées des jeux de données rasters composant la série UrbIS.\nCe service est mis à jour de manière ponctuelle à partir des couches analogues du Service de visualisation - Raster. L'usage de ce service est recommandé pour tous les viewers et applications front-end."@fr, "This tiled view service makes it possible to obtain georeferenced tiles from the raster datasets that make up the UrbIS series.\nThis service is updated periodically based on the corresponding layers of the View service - Raster. The use of this service is recommended for all viewers and front-end applications."@en, "Dieser Kachelansichtsdienst ermöglicht es, georeferenzierte Kacheln aus den Raster-Datasets der UrbIS-Serie zu erhalten.\nDieser Dienst wird regelmäßig auf der Grundlage der entsprechenden Ebenen des View-Dienstes - Raster - aktualisiert. Die Nutzung dieses Dienstes wird allen Zuschauern und Frontend-Anwendungen empfohlen."@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-05-22T07:40:54.000Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://org.belgif.be/id/CbeRegisteredEntity/0240678477>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://eurovoc.europa.eu/4426>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/7102>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/theme/oi>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialScope/regional>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialDataServiceCategory/infoMapAccessService>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/ENVI>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://datastore.brussels/web/data/service/da181eac-0756-11f1-8373-900f0cda5d5b>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> _:b277831_b277830_b277829_df_12_69770;
