<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#2fd783eb7aa42ed91787ca8fa0368068>.
<#2fd783eb7aa42ed91787ca8fa0368068> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/dataset/brussels/0e039770-722b-11ed-b593-00090ffe0001>;
