<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#0152afb8ebbf12269eee733f7a83b839>.
<#0152afb8ebbf12269eee733f7a83b839> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://metadata.vlaanderen.be/srv/resources/services/61d463a6-07c1-4f9e-bc7d-47846470e718>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-06-15T15:38:07.618Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#0152afb8ebbf12269eee733f7a83b839> {
<https://metadata.vlaanderen.be/srv/resources/services/61d463a6-07c1-4f9e-bc7d-47846470e718> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#DataService>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/NLD>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "61d463a6-07c1-4f9e-bc7d-47846470e718";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Sociale Zekerheid - GeefAttestWerkloosheid - Versie 01.00"@nl, "Sécurité sociale - GeefAttestUnemployment - Version 01.00"@fr-t-nl, "Soziale Sicherheit - GeefAttestArbeitslosigkeit - Version 01.00"@de-t-nl, "Social Security - GeefAttestUnemployment - Version 01.00"@en-t-nl;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Het doel van deze dienst is het beschikbaar stellen van de attesten in verband met werklozen.Deze informatie komt van de KSZ, die op zijn beurt weer gevoed wordt door de Rijksdienst Voor Arbeidsvoorziening (RVA)."@nl, "L'objectif de ce service est de mettre à disposition les certificats relatifs aux chômeurs.Ces informations proviennent de la KSZ, qui est à son tour alimentée par le Service national de l'emploi (RVA)."@fr-t-nl, "Zweck dieses Dienstes ist es, die Bescheinigungen über Arbeitslose zur Verfügung zu stellen. Diese Informationen stammen aus dem KSZ, das wiederum von der Nationalen Arbeitsverwaltung (RVA) gespeist wird."@de-t-nl, "The purpose of this service is to make the certificates related to the unemployed available.This information comes from the KSZ, which in turn is fed by the National Employment Service (RVA)."@en-t-nl;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#identifier> _:b278116_b278115_b278114_df_12_69919, _:b278116_b278115_b278114_df_12_69920;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#version> "01.00";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://org.belgif.be/id/CbeEstablishmentUnit/2256180804>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> <https://org.belgif.be/id/CbeEstablishmentUnit/2256180804>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/NON_PUBLIC>;
    <http://data.europa.eu/r5r/applicableLegislation> <http://data.europa.eu/eli/reg/2022/868/oj>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Rijksdienst Voor Arbeidsvoorziening"@nl, "MAGDA"@nl, "sociale zekerheid"@nl, "Kruispuntbank Sociale Zekerheid"@nl;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/HEAL>, <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/GOVE>;
