<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#00347b533318c33d349863a89e9fb63f>.
<#00347b533318c33d349863a89e9fb63f> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://metadata.vlaanderen.be/srv/resources/services/50789ab0-f838-4d9a-916f-c38dc6e3c908>;
