_:b278500_b278499_b278498_df_12_70194 a <http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#Identifier>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "https://metadata.vlaanderen.be/srv/doc/service/dc15c47c-daa0-4253-b717-03dad25c5267".
_:b278500_b278499_b278498_df_12_70195 a <http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#Identifier>;
