    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialDataServiceCategory/infoCoverageAccessService>, <https://metadata.vlaanderen.be/id/GDI-Vlaanderen-Service-Types/OGCWCS>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/ENVI>;
