<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#3f9f8d722e83476346024931e45a0e45>.
<#3f9f8d722e83476346024931e45a0e45> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://metadata.vlaanderen.be/srv/resources/services/1ec4a229-b367-35d1-be24-c687a64014f1>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-06-15T15:38:08.941Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#3f9f8d722e83476346024931e45a0e45> {
