<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#dc4348985ca985150ba2d166cc125bbe>.
<#dc4348985ca985150ba2d166cc125bbe> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://metadata.omgeving.vlaanderen.be/srv/resources/services/f320185a-6613-4230-9ada-146f99a00e24>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-06-15T15:38:09.196Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#dc4348985ca985150ba2d166cc125bbe> {
<https://metadata.omgeving.vlaanderen.be/srv/resources/services/f320185a-6613-4230-9ada-146f99a00e24> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#DataService>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "f320185a-6613-4230-9ada-146f99a00e24";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "OGC API Features - Publieke Download Service van Vlaamse Overheid - beleidsdomein Omgeving - samenwerkingsverband MercatorNet"@nl, "Fonctionnalités API de l'OGC - Service public de téléchargement du gouvernement flamand - domaine politique Environnement - Partenariat MercatorNet"@fr-t-nl, "OGC API Features - Öffentlicher Download Service der Flämischen Regierung - Politikbereich Umwelt - MercatorNet Partnerschaft"@de-t-nl, "OGC API Features - Public Download Service of the Flemish Government - policy area Environment - MercatorNet partnership"@en-t-nl;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Alle kaartlagen van MercatorNet kunnen via de OGC API Features opgevraagd worden. Deze API is een moderne variant van de Web Features Service API die beter aansluit op hedendaagse standaarden voor ReSTful web services. Zo is er bijvoorbeeld een openapi beschrijving van de web service ter vervanging van het GetCapabilities document bij WFS."@nl, "Toutes les couches de carte MercatorNet sont accessibles via les fonctionnalités de l'API OGC. Cette API est une version moderne de l'API Web Features Service qui correspond mieux aux normes actuelles pour les services Web ReSTful. Par exemple, il existe une description openapi du service Web pour remplacer le document GetCapabilities à WFS."@fr-t-nl, "Alle MercatorNet-Kartenebenen können über die OGC-API-Funktionen aufgerufen werden. Diese API ist eine moderne Version der Web Features Service API, die besser zu den heutigen Standards für ReSTful-Webdienste passt. Beispielsweise gibt es eine openapi-Beschreibung des Webdienstes, die das GetCapabilities-Dokument bei WFS ersetzt."@de-t-nl, "All MercatorNet map layers can be accessed via the OGC API Features. This API is a modern version of the Web Features Service API that better fits today's standards for ReSTful web services. For example, there is an openapi description of the web service to replace the GetCapabilities document at WFS."@en-t-nl;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2023-03-04"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#identifier> _:b278899_b278898_b278897_df_12_70478;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://org.belgif.be/id/CbeEstablishmentUnit/2199336923>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/conformsTo> <https://data.vlaanderen.be/id/concept/dataserviceprotocol/OGC:OGC-API-Features>, <https://data.vlaanderen.be/id/concept/dataserviceprotocol/OGC:OGC-API-Features-landingpage>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/id/document/tg/sds>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://data.europa.eu/r5r/applicableLegislation> <http://data.europa.eu/eli/reg/2009/976/oj>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/rights> <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/rights/f011858c7e4c5d141b423b4302e9bfc0783c3a5f>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "OGC API"@nl, "Download Service"@nl, "MercatorNet"@nl, "Vlaanderen"@nl, "OpenbareMetadata"@nl;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialDataServiceCategory/infoFeatureAccessService>, <https://metadata.vlaanderen.be/id/GDI-Vlaanderen-Service-Types/OGCWFS>;
