_:b278977_b278976_b278975_df_12_70539 a <http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#Identifier>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "https://metadata.vlaanderen.be/srv/doc/service/21fe103b-c01d-416d-8c19-c5b82ae00461".
